            "answer_2": "<p>Return eligibility depends on the product and whether it was made or modified specifically for you. Review the policy attached to your order and contact us before returning any furniture.</p>",
            "question_3": "Are grain and color variations defects?",
            "answer_3": "<p>No. Natural grain, knots, tone shifts, and organic edges are part of each piece's character. If you are concerned about structure or workmanship, send clear photographs for assessment.</p>"
