            "question_1": "What can be customized?",
            "answer_1": "<p>Depending on the design, we can explore dimensions, wood selection, finish, proportions, and project-specific forms. Feasibility is confirmed after we understand the space and intended use.</p>",
            "question_2": "How does a bespoke commission begin?",
            "answer_2": "<p>Start with a consultation and share your room, approximate dimensions, preferred product type, budget range, timeline, and reference images. We then define the scope before production is approved.</p>",
