            "heading": "Care instructions",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "open_first_question": false,
            "question_1": "How should I clean natural wood furniture?",
            "answer_1": "<p>Dust with a soft, dry cloth and wipe spills promptly. Avoid abrasive pads, harsh household chemicals, and prolonged moisture unless your piece's care guide states otherwise.</p>",
            "question_2": "Where should I place my furniture?",
            "answer_2": "<p>Keep natural wood away from sustained direct sunlight, heating vents, and abrupt humidity changes. A stable interior environment helps the material age more evenly.</p>",
            "question_3": "Can a WRYDECO piece be refinished or repaired?",
            "answer_3": "<p>Many solid wood surfaces can be professionally maintained or restored. Contact us with photographs before using oils, waxes, fillers, or refinishing products so we can advise based on the original finish.</p>"
