            "answer_1": "<p>A consultation is useful when you are choosing between pieces, planning a high-value purchase, working with unusual dimensions, or considering a bespoke commission.</p>",
            "question_2": "What should I prepare?",
            "answer_2": "<p>Bring room photographs, approximate dimensions, access notes, your preferred piece or product type, budget range, timeline, and any visual references that clarify the atmosphere you want.</p>",
